title: "saia-python"
abstract: >-
  A Python wrapper for the GWDG SAIA (Scalable AI Accelerator) platform REST API,
  providing object-oriented and functional access to chat completions, voice
  transcription/translation, document conversion, ARCANA (RAG / knowledge bases),
  and an OpenAI SDK compatibility layer.
